# AI Model API keys (required)
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=your_deepseek_api_key

PREFERRED_AI_MODEL="deepseek-chat"
PREFERRED_AI_URL="https://api.deepseek.com"

# Tavily API key (optional, for enhanced news search)
TAVILY_API_KEY=your_tavily_api_key

# Alpaca Markets API credentials
ALPACA_API_KEY_LLM_AGENT=your_alpaca_api_key
ALPACA_API_SECRET_LLM_AGENT=your_alpaca_secret_key
ALPACA_PAPER_TRADING_LLM_AGENT=true

# Alpaca configuration
ALPACA_BASE_URL=https://paper-api.alpaca.markets

# Backtesting mode (true/false)
BACKTEST=false

# Polygon.io API key (for stock screening and historical data)
POLYGON_API_KEY=your_polygon_api_key_here

## Extending the Project

You can easily extend this project by:

- Adding more data sources (e.g., options data, insider trading)
- Creating a command-line interface to specify tickers at runtime
- Comparing multiple stocks simultaneously
- Storing analysis results in a database for historical comparison
- Building a web interface to visualize the results
- Implementing more sophisticated short-selling risk metrics

